data.description: Seller will consider Buyer Closing Cost help with an offer on this Home!! 4 Bedrooms,3 Baths, 2 Very Large Living Areas, Big Laundry Room, and 2860sqft of Living Space!!! Two Isolated Bedroom Suites..The Master Suite and a Mother-In-Law Suite..The Large Lot allows enough space for 2 Large Backyards!! The Unique Cul-de-sac provides Extra Privacy and Security. All the rooms are Big with Large Closets. New Carpet in both Isolated Bedroom Suites and New Garage Doors!! Seller will also paint the Bedroom walls the color of Buyers' choosing....This is a Must See to Appreciate All this Home has to Offer!!!     This floorplan layout would even be Great for an Air-bnb!!!!
